<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/account/form.css" />
<script src="/javascripts/account/form.js"></script>
<section>
  <div class="mb-4">
    <h1>
      <span>팥붕슈붕에 가입하기</span>
    </h1>
  </div>
  <form class="needs-validation" novalidate>
    <div class="mb-5">
      <label for="phone" class="form-label">전화번호</label>
      <input
        type="text"
        class="form-control"
        id="phone"
        placeholder="숫자만 입력해주세요"
        required
        oninput="onInputPhone(this)"
        pattern="\d{2,3}-\d{3,4}-\d{4}"
      />
      <div class="invalid-feedback">전화번호를 정확히 입력해주세요</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-4">
      <label for="nickname" class="form-label">닉네임</label>
      <input
        type="text"
        class="form-control"
        id="nickname"
        aria-describedby="nicknameHelpBlock"
        required
        pattern=".{3,20}"
      />
      <div id="nicknameHelpBlock" class="form-text">
        팥붕슈붕에서 활동할 때 사용할 별명이에요. 언제든지 다시 바꿀 수 있어요.
      </div>
      <div class="invalid-feedback">닉네임은 3자 이상 20자 이하여야 해요</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mb-5">
      <label for="password" class="form-label">비밀번호</label>
      <input
        type="password"
        class="form-control"
        id="password"
        aria-describedby="passwordHelpBlock"
        required
        pattern=".{8,}"
      />
      <div id="passwordHelpBlock" class="form-text">
        비밀번호는 8자 이상이어야 해요
      </div>
      <div class="invalid-feedback">8자 이상의 비밀번호를 입력해주세요</div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">가입하기</button>
      <span>계정이 있으신가요? <a href="/account/signin">로그인하기</a></span>
    </div>
  </form>
</section>
